        The Grove School of Engineering of The City College of New York


We are actively looking for additional TFP sponsors, who may, for example, =

help to   =20
subsidise attendance by research students. If you or your organisation=20
might be    =20
willing to sponsor TFP, or if you know someone who might be willing to do=20
so, please =20
do not hesitate to contact the Program Chair, Marco T. Morazan, or the=20
Symposium Chair,    =20
Henrik Nilsson. Your students will be grateful!    =20



